---
title: Middle Eastern Pork & Goat Cheese Sumac Potatoes with Eggplant, Tomato-Mint Salad & Garlic Dip
description: We could pretend the main attraction here is the tender roasted eggplant with refreshing mint, or the succulent spiced pork, but that’d be dishonest. If we’re being real, the magic in this dish is the stunning sumac roasted potatoes delicately topped with a smattering of goat cheese. It's crispy, filling, earthy and indulgent. We could go on and on, but we’ll let you get on with the eating. Bon appetite!
